org.eclipse.xtext.xbase.lib

Annotation Type Pure


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={CONSTRUCTOR,METHOD})
@Documented
@Beta
@GwtCompatible
public @interface Pure
    Whether the constructor or method causes any side-effects to non-local state. On Inlined methods this is means the compiler cannot use the resulting Java expression as a statement.
    Since:
    2.3
    Author:
    Sven Efftinge - Initial contribution and API
